<HEADLINE>
<P>
EXPLOSION AT CLUB KILLS 12 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BRUSSELS 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An explosion in the cellar of a Brussels shooting club on Sunday killed 12 
people and seriously injured at least three, firefighters at the scene said. 
The cause of the blast was not known. 
</P>
</TEXT>
